---
title: Chilli Garlic Prawn Noodles with teriyaki veg and crunchy peanuts
description: The wonderful thing about these garlic prawn noodles is that you can customise them to suit your individual taste. If you're a fan of heat, add plenty of chilli flakes for extra bite. If you like things on the milder side, simply be more reserved with your chilli flake shake!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R11_W37_IE_IEXCLS15923-2_Main__10high-18de6e1b.jpg
